Student Enrollment System

Description
A Java-based application that allows students to enroll in courses while administrators manage student registrations.

Technologies Used
- Java
- Java Swing / JavaFX

My Role
Designed and developed the full system including student and admin functionality.

Installation
1. Clone the repository
2. Open in NetBeans or IntelliJ
3. Run the project

Usage
- Students can enroll in courses
- Admins can manage enrollments

